				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Ok.  That &quot;Jackolm&quot; guy in freeport---&gt;BAD IDEA.  As soon as you attack him and run up the stairs that you are speaking of, and go to drop down off the ledge, the two women there aggro on you.  I know from personal experience.  Both these two women hit me for almost 250dmg each (thank god they didn't each double attack).  I dropped down, and Jackolm did as advertised.  He ran back down the stairs, hit me for about 40-50dmg, and I died.<BR>
<BR>
He's not very tough, however those two women that constantly stand there will make this camp near impossible for anyone who is not able to solo both of them as well (conned red to lvl35).
