				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Ok, that was pretty quick and detailed, But I think you could use some better Exp spots, you did great till 20 lol<BR>
So, What I did at 20 is, head to South Karana and head to the Hermit, Sorry i forgot the LOC but if you go to the Far <BR>
Western wall... and keep your eye to the Left you'll see a Building sorrounded in a Rock Wall, This Hermit is insane Exp,<BR>
i got lvl 22-24 in a day and a half.. ONLY SOLO him , even at 20 if your a necro he's a peice of cake, just go near the<BR>
House he'll automatically start comin for you, your pet jumps on him and hopefully you'll have him targeted... Stack DoTs<BR>
and Fear, he'll run into the house wall and be stuck while your pet mauls on him.<BR>
When you got to 24 this is where you sky rocket to 30, Head on over to the Treants,<BR>
Best Grouped with a Mage or Wizard or both till 27, Then try to Keep the spawn split with just you and the other person.<BR>
If you can Keep it down with a Wiz you'll level so fast .. i think i was gettin a bubble and a half an hour and the loot <BR>
is insane.. i think its 1-8p the max i've gotten is 24 plat off one pop, they drop 16Plat Staffs depending on your Charisma<BR>
and can drop up for 4p and 40gold...I made 1k plat in about 3 lvls.. So finding a Wizard is vital for those trips to the bank.<BR>
<BR>
Soon as your 30, you Can fight the Sisters till 32 or so... Then leave them, because the druids in WC<BR>
are FARRRR Better Exp and will level you up fastttt... Soon as you get to 34 killin them becomes beyond easy... VoS + 2 Nukes <BR>
and whatever dmg your pet does will kill them everytime.. thats about 2 bubbles of mana at 34.<BR>
<BR>
After gettin to 37 you should solo the 2 spawn to launch to lvl 40. Soon as you hit lvl 40 Head to Oasis and Solo Spectre's<BR>
there's someone down there fightin them or lookin for a group.. Just offer to take 2 Specs a spawn<BR>
and they take the other 2 and they'll most likely be happy.. Be sure to SOLO Because<BR>
they are beyond easy with Invoke/VoS/Boil/Vamp Curse and a Nuke or 2...<BR>
<BR>
Specs will take you to 45, Where ' Overthere ' in Kunark becomes your new Leveling spot till 50.<BR>
Go to the Temple i forgot the name =( and use it as your pull spot, Keep pet at the temple,<BR>
and Pull back to the temple, Rhino's literally have no chance of winnin, So thats pretty much it =)<BR>
<BR>
Happy Necroing
